CHANGELOG
=========

0.5.0 (unreleased)
------------------

- No changes yet.


0.4.1 (2014-07-16)
------------------

- Disable MOMT flow if no specific or default number is set
- Add the --fd argument to let circus spawn the socket
- Add the /api-specs url for videur
- Really fix the decrypt error
- Update configuration example
- Install fake_dynamo only if needed


0.4.0 (2014-07-15)
------------------

- Fix 0.3.1 loadtest decrypt error
- Add BeepSend SMS Gateway
- Add SMS Gateway fallback mechanism
- Moved to AWS-SDK to handle STS support
- Make the loadtest Python 2.6 compatible


0.3.1 (2014-07-08)
------------------

- Fix MSISDN certificate generation
- Improve loadtests debugging
- Change loadtests configuration from duration to hits


0.3.0 (2014-07-03)
------------------

- Add loadtests
- Remove res.on("header") deprecation
- Graceful shutdown of the server ok SIGTERM
- Manage l10n translation
- Handle Hawk auth behind and HTTPS ELB
- Add a DynamoDB persistent storage backend
- Handle https and http agents configuration
- Store encrypted MSISDN number into the database


0.2.0 (2014-06-06)
------------------

- Add the SMS MOMT protocol
- Rewrite the API flows
  - POST /discover
  - POST /register
  - POST /unregister
  - POST /sms/mt/verify
  - SMS /sms/momt/verify
  - POST /sms/verify_code
  - POST /certificat/sign
- Use the FxA error format
- Use Hawk Session
- Implement BrowserID IdP well-known info.
- Allow a limited number of retries for a verification code
- Return the right moVerifier wrt the MCC/MNC code
- Manage Hawk session expiration


0.1.0 (2014-05-06)
------------------

- Get a first PoC working
- Add the SMS MT protocol
    - /register
    - /unregister
    - /sms/verify
    - /sms/verify_code
    - /sms/resend_code
